1. Our algorithm is able to discover relevant news articles in association with the given stock time series GOOG (Google company).¶

2. The algorithm is completely data-driven as it was trained purely based on the general news collected from Thomson Reuters along with a stock price time series under interesting. Neither company name nor pre-selected news articles have been used in training.¶

3. Following demonstrates its performance on the testing dataset, i.e., year 2013 when there is at least one groundtruth news article (for evaluation).¶

4. First column show the news index, 2nd column show the attention mass associated with each news headlines shown in 3rd column. Higher attention mass imply more relevant news associated with the time series¶
